OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781089372
OL,3,CFake phone chargers sold by online can
OL,4,Ccause electrocution, Which? warns
OL,6,FFaulty phone chargers are being sold
OL,7,Fonline by major retailers, consumer
OL,8,Fwatchdog Which? has warned.
OL,10,FWhich? researchers bought 15 USB phone
OL,11,Fchargers from seven online
OL,12,Fmarketplaces and tested them to
OL,13,Fdetermine whether they were safe and
OL,14,Flegal to sell in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
