FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781089372
OL,3,CFake phone chargers sold by online can
OL,4,Ccause electrocution, Which? warns
OL,6,FNine of the chargers, bought from
OL,7,FAmazon, including Amazon Haul, as well
OL,8,Fas AliExpress, B&Q Marketplace, and
OL,9,FDebenhams Marketplace, were so badly
OL,10,Fmanufactured that anyone using them
OL,11,Fwas at risk of being electrocuted,
OL,12,Fthey found.
OL,14,FEight of the chargers also posed fire
OL,15,Fand explosion risks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781089372
OL,3,CFake phone chargers sold by online can
OL,4,Ccause electrocution, Which? warns
OL,6,FAll 15 of the chargers Which? bought
OL,7,Fwere missing key information on the
OL,8,Fpackaging, the charger itself or in
OL,9,Fthe documentation provided, which
OL,10,Fshould have prevented them from being
OL,11,Flegally sold in the UK.
OL,13,FOne of the chargers, sold as an
OL,14,F'Apple' USB-C 35W Power Adaptor
OL,15,Fcharger for #11.99 on eBay and marked
OL,16,Fwith the Apple logo, was found to be a
OL,17,Fdangerous fake.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781089372
OL,3,CFake phone chargers sold by online can
OL,4,Ccause electrocution, Which? warns
OL,6,FResearchers opened the charger's case
OL,7,Fand found a lump of modelling clay
OL,8,Finside, which they believe was used to
OL,9,Fgive the charger a more weighty,
OL,10,Frobust and genuine feel.
OL,12,FOne customer who bought the charger
OL,13,Fposted on the listing to say that it
OL,14,Fhad overloaded and ruined their iPad
OL,15,Fand phone, both of which had stopped
OL,16,Fcharging.
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
