FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781089372
OL,3,CFake phone chargers sold by online can
OL,4,Ccause electrocution, Which? warns
OL,6,FHead of Consumer Protection Policy at
OL,7,FWhich?, Sue Davies, has warned that
OL,8,Fbadly designed electricals can have
OL,9,Ffatal consequences.
OL,11,F"Online marketplaces have known about
OL,12,Fthe danger of knock-off chargers for
OL,13,Fthe better part of a decade, but
OL,14,Fconsumers continue to be placed at
OL,15,Frisk," she said.
OL,17,FDavies has called on the government to
OL,18,Fupdate product safety legislation and
OL,19,Fimpose tougher regulations on
OL,20,Fretailers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
