FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781089372
OL,3,CFake phone chargers sold by online can
OL,4,Ccause electrocution, Which? warns
OL,6,F"By making online marketplaces legally
OL,7,Fresponsible for unsafe products, the
OL,8,FGovernment can set a world-leading
OL,9,Fstandard for product safety in the
OL,10,Fdigital age."
OL,12,FAll the retailers involved said they
OL,13,Fhad removed the listings in question,
OL,14,Feither proactively or as a result of
OL,15,FWhich?'s findings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
